caption: (Translated by Google) A well-prepared meal has delicate flavors that must be retained in the mouth to appreciate them and it is here in this beautiful restaurant where I was able to savor the delicious, the good, the rich, the tasty, the exquisite, the appetizing of their food. ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ comfortable prices and above all the Attention is extremely very good God bless 🙏 the staff and their Owners.  (Original) Una comida bien preparada tiene sabores delicados qué hay que retener en la boca para apreciarlos y es aquí en este Hermoso restaurante donde pude saborear lo Delicioso, lo bueno , lo rico, lo sabroso ,lo exquisito,lo apetitoso, de su comida . ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️precios cómodos y sobre todo la Atención es sumamente muy buena Dios bendiga 🙏al personal y sus Propietarios.
